---
title: Oven-baked Bacon Risotto				 with torn mozzarella and basil garnish
description: Though not cooked in the traditional way, this dish retains all the hallmarks of a classic risotto. The great news is its oven-baked nature offers a less hands-on approach to dinnertime. Multitaskers rejoice!
